text: Space Oddity is the sixth studio album by David Bowie. The album was released on November 10, 1972. ==Track listing== # Space Oddity – 5:17 # Unwashed and Somewhat Slightly Dazed – 6:53 # Letter to Hermione – 2:36 # Cygnet Committee – 9:35 # Janine – 3:25 # An Occasional Dream – 3:02 # The Wild Eyed Boy From Freecloud – 4:52 # God Knows I’m Good – 3:21 # Memory of a Free Festival – 7:10 ==References== Category:1972 albums Category:RCA Records albums Category:David Bowie albums
